{"tid":1200094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係俾胡椒噴到既話點算好？","createTime":"2019-06-10T16:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T16:35:20.000Z","uid":168228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e03aebe36dcb68da981d1bb5a0164d793f02f7","tid":1200094,"uid":168228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"有無咩方法舒緩？"},{"pid":"989eb5a66b66ae523c0d4120855a599037e52a2e","tid":1200094,"uid":138836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:35:20.000Z","msg":"1.先用紙巾/紗布印乾,印到幾多得幾多,即刻沖水會將胡椒擴散去其他地方<br />\n2.大量沖水 e.g噴中上臂 你可以瞓低沖 唔好等啲水流過全身先落地<br />\n<br />\n依家啲胡椒噴霧用人工合成 用唔用奶沖其實冇咩分別<br />\n到時都唔會有咁多奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得返到屋企要印乾埋頭皮同頭髮！如果唔喺一沖涼嗰陣入眼就會好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}